Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.46,0:00:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互道初次见面的时候总会有种心跳的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.71,0:00:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人与人的相遇是美妙的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.34,0:00:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们要把这个瞬间当作宝物来对待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.65,0:00:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并铭记于心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.40,0:00:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人害羞的台词 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窗户 什么时候打开的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.49,0:01:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.39,0:01:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.51,0:02:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.35,0:02:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着各种各样的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.60,0:02:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉到新的一天开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.82,0:02:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.62,0:03:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了 灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.19,0:03:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.31,0:03:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.47,0:03:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好 这里是亚利亚公司 多谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.07,0:03:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好 多谢来电
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.70,0:03:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.33,0:03:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晓先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.74,0:03:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得本人想要听艾莉西亚的语音留言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.05,0:03:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而特地打电话来…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.57,0:03:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要妨碍我？鬓子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.66,0:03:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是什么鬓子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 就是鬓子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.70,0:03:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你还留着那个长鬓的话就一直都是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.38,0:03:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了那不是鬓角了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.84,0:03:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果您想预约凤尾舟的话 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本大爷很忙 没空和鬓子谈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.44,0:03:54.32,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(320,270)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那份 美妙的奇迹…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.27,0:04:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里 新威尼斯的春天就快结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.39,0:04:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从我第一天到AQUA的日子算起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.11,0:04:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转眼已经快20个月了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.86,0:04:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以AQUA的年历来说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.48,0:04:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有4个月左右就满整整一年了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.59,0:04:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二个夏天也就快来临了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.95,0:04:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸟离开巢穴时 也是这种心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是AQUA
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.85,0:05:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个城市就是新威尼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.22,0:05:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的天地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该说是和我想像中的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是超乎我的想像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.89,0:05:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一见钟情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.88,0:05:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个城市 我一定会让你们看到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将成为一个出色的领航员
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.70,0:05:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好 多谢来电 这里是亚利亚公司
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.64,0:05:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我想坐艾莉西亚小姐的凤尾舟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.26,0:05:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.29,0:05:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何我都想坐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.16,0:05:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预约都满了 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？那么其他人也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 这里只有我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我因为还是半熟手 一个人不能接待客人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.69,0:05:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.36,0:05:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.95,0:05:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我是个出色的领航员的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果不是艾莉西亚前辈的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许客人也无法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.48,0:06:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我们去练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.87,0:06:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.07,0:06:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是去练习吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.87,0:06:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么快点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.22,0:06:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是半熟手 不能接待…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.74,0:06:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始我们就是朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.68,0:06:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是客人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要喊了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.40,0:06:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喊什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.90,0:06:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绑架啊 来人啊 救命啊 就这么叫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:06:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.36,0:07:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 这是我想出来的不让船摇晃的练习
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是晃得很厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.07,0:07:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢坐凤尾舟吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能不太喜欢 而且又慢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.83,0:07:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这个孩子是刚才打电话来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.84,0:08:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道 你是从地球来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.86,0:08:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.01,0:08:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前也是住在地球上的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.11,0:08:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人来的？这是不可能的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和爸爸妈妈一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.84,0:08:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新威尼斯怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.44,0:08:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和地球比起来是不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有汽车 出门几乎都是用走路的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜也是自己去买材料回来自己做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.09,0:08:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凤尾舟按惯例也是自己来划
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.14,0:08:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是累人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我很喜欢像这样全部都要自己来做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.31,0:08:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地球上是做不到的 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.39,0:08:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能告诉我你的名字吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫水无灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.77,0:08:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.87,0:08:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.92,0:08:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要坐我的凤尾舟？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.55,0:08:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在审问我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.87,0:09:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然和听说的不一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.13,0:09:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 蓝华
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.68,0:09:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子不是游客
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.61,0:09:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的朋友 叫小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从地球来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不就是白坐船吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.74,0:09:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 如你所说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.19,0:09:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快点下船
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.02,0:09:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个谁划得好？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问谁划得好的话 当然是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 请你来划
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.69,0:09:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.07,0:09:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华 做朋友又没什么关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.33,0:09:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.56,0:10:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 好不容易相识一场 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 蓝华 我们去看艾莉西亚前辈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.35,0:10:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华 你真的很喜欢艾莉西亚前辈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.31,0:10:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.03,0:10:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是晃得很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.17,0:10:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为准确的时间和愉快的交谈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.72,0:10:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是姬屋公司的格言啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.23,0:10:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AQUA从被改造到适合人类居住已约有150年了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时至今日 被人称之为「水之星球」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.02,0:10:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而新威尼斯则以过去地球上的城市威尼斯为原型
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.36,0:10:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你突然之间说什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.53,0:10:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想有个导游会比较有趣点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.60,0:10:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你说的一点都没劲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且对白坐船的也不用服务得如此周到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.14,0:10:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 好不容易来这一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.21,0:11:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是想让她喜欢上新威尼斯再回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.80,0:11:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢这个城市吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.80,0:11:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.84,0:11:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初只是向往着要成为帅气的领航员才来这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.17,0:11:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在却越来越喜欢AQUA和新威尼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.73,0:11:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不方便的交通 悠闲的时间 这些全部都喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.48,0:11:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个城市 一定是由奇迹所构成的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇迹？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 在曾经没有空气和水的这颗星球上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.31,0:11:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建造这座城市的人们的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.49,0:11:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,众多回忆和思念聚集而产生出的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.35,0:11:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美妙的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.12,0:11:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的相遇也许也是奇迹之一呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.24,0:11:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人害羞的台词 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.94,0:12:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卖烤奶油马铃薯的船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.98,0:12:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤奶油马铃薯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.66,0:12:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓 在家里也吃过 并不怎么喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.16,0:12:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.49,0:12:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和在地球上吃起来的感觉完全不一样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.76,0:12:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还是尝尝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有钱？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.93,0:12:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.81,0:12:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么说呢 有钱却白坐船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.52,0:12:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也太狡猾了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.11,0:12:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我们也不能收她的钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.02,0:12:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.02,0:12:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马铃薯好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.41,0:13:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地球上卖的一般是切成小块的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃起来好像很不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.71,0:14:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.25,0:14:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？多谢夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我们出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.44,0:14:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长 我们要出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.38,0:14:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.85,0:14:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.40,0:14:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.91,0:14:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想应该让熟练的人来划会比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.75,0:14:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的 灯里还有秘密绝招呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.76,0:14:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使出全力吧 灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.07,0:14:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我要出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.94,0:15:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为灯里她在地球作练习时
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.95,0:15:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阴差阳错地学会了逆划
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.46,0:15:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在逆划的时候她可是无敌的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.07,0:15:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样划没问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.19,0:15:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.02,0:15:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 就这样笔直过去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.29,0:15:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微左边点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.69,0:15:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.20,0:16:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.90,0:16:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.42,0:16:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太酷了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然采取了意外的举动 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.51,0:17:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢 艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.94,0:17:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 蓝华也在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.68,0:17:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.65,0:17:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子叫小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.77,0:17:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.82,0:17:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.14,0:17:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我们也做朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.54,0:17:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.52,0:17:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 再见了 小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.43,0:17:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.23,0:17:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.90,0:17:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.84,0:17:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱 你一直想见艾莉西亚前辈的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.09,0:17:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.36,0:17:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上打电话来的就是小爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.29,0:17:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说想要坐艾莉西亚前辈的凤尾舟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.31,0:18:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这里之前 我非常讨厌AQUA和新威尼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为之前我姐姐的新婚旅行就是来的这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.51,0:18:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年龄差得很大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.63,0:18:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 所以她一直把我当小孩子对待
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.51,0:18:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行回来后 就一直对我说AQUA的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.99,0:18:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然喜欢姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.42,0:18:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我稍微有点讨厌她的夸耀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.29,0:18:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我连AQUA和新威尼斯也讨厌起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.19,0:18:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是不能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 你今天为什么来这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.31,0:18:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想如果实际来一次的话 也许会喜欢上这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.98,0:18:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就拜托了爸爸妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.44,0:18:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他们刚带我来到这里的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.12,0:18:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到处都非常无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.29,0:18:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我也坐过其它的凤尾舟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.26,0:18:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉不过如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.42,0:18:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我想说 还是非得坐姐姐最为夸耀的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.75,0:19:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚的凤尾舟才行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是却坐不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.53,0:19:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是你就决定坐灯里的凤尾舟对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.04,0:19:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.66,0:19:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是今天能坐上你们的船真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.26,0:19:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤奶油马铃薯非常好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.07,0:19:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逆划也非常有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.79,0:19:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去后我也要向姐姐夸耀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.27,0:19:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想 你姐姐并不是在夸耀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.40,0:19:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许她是想告诉小爱AQUA上的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.80,0:19:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 你想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.07,0:19:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是也想告诉别人你所喜欢的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.82,0:19:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是对于你喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.96,0:19:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就想告诉姐姐今天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.11,0:19:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.71,0:19:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为什么 忽然想听姐姐的闲谈了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.36,0:20:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了灯里你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.34,0:20:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来也许有一天 我也会喜欢上这座城市的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.71,0:20:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从讨厌转变成喜欢 也许是奇迹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.50,0:20:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人害羞的台词 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.47,0:20:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.34,0:20:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是给各位添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.86,0:20:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道该怎么道歉才好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 完全没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.72,0:20:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 真的今天就要离开这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.54,0:20:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想在明天的午休时间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.06,0:20:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去拜托艾莉西亚前辈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.06,0:20:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们下次再来这里的话 我一定会想办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.56,0:20:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会发邮件给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.95,0:20:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.30,0:20:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.97,0:20:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.47,0:21:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次来的时候 我还想坐灯里你的凤尾舟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.96,0:21:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.61,0:21:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 你要尽快成为出色的领航员哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.80,0:21:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.78,0:21:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 还有这个 请交给艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.19,0:21:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.61,0:21:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.31,0:21:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两位我还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.35,0:21:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在凤尾舟上开始吵架的新婚夫妇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.36,0:21:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在旅行中 第一次了解到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.94,0:21:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此所不了解的讨厌的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.99,0:21:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不知所措呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.18,0:21:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来和好如初了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.17,0:21:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 虽然那时候真的很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.19,0:21:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去好幸福的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.59,0:21:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.21,0:22:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从讨厌转变成喜欢 虽然需要点努力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.11,0:22:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能做到这点的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.34,0:22:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所喜欢的人就会成为你所珍惜的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.08,0:22:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所珍惜的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.46,0:22:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份奇迹 能够靠努力来获取啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.68,0:22:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.30,0:22:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱的奇迹也许是靠她自己得来的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.48,0:22:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 想变得更喜欢姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.94,0:22:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是小爱所带来的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.88,0:24:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈 今天也是美好的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.89,0:24:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 灯里你的哪一天不是美好的一天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.28,0:24:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.01,0:24:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 特别的日子…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.90,0:24:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们一起度过美好的时光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.21,0:01:32.10,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}頬をなでる 優しい風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.84,0:01:41.27,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}波音に 揺られて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.61,0:01:50.88,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}体の中 ほどけてゆくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.46,0:02:01.64,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}目を閉じて 見えてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.25,0:02:09.90,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}風の行く道が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.14,0:02:20.00,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}さあ 漕ぎ出そう 光る波へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:29.16,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}笑顏が すぐ こぼれる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.52,0:02:39.32,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}ねえ 伝えよう このときめき
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.62,0:02:49.92,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}風にのって あなたのもとへ 行くわ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:54.12,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}ウンディーネ
