Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.84,0:01:41.27,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}在海浪的歌声中摇曳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.61,0:01:50.88,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}慢慢地 融入身体里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.46,0:02:01.64,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}闭上双眼 看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.25,0:02:09.90,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}是风的轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.14,0:02:20.00,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}来 让我们出发 向着闪亮的波涛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:29.16,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}脸上的笑容 从未消失
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.52,0:02:39.32,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}快 传达到彼方 把这份感动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.62,0:02:49.92,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}托付给清风 带到你的身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:54.12,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}水之精灵
